<p><placeName>Herculanium </placeName><date when="1820-02-02">Feby 2th 1820</date></p>
<p>Dear <persName>Son</persName></p>

<p>I have only time to say that your Dear <persName>mother </persName>is as well as could
be expected I have lately returned home and found your letter 
inclose you have 20 Dollars its the best and only money now to be had
in this County I hope It may do you some good Next mail I hope
I may send you 50 Dollars to discharge all your bill I have sent
to <placeName>Washington </placeName>to have arrangements made for you on board the
Navy by <date n="04-xx-1820">April </date>so that you must make all the deligence you can</p>

<p>God Bless you and Keep you my Dear <persName>Son </persName>Your Aff <persName>Father</persName></p>

<p><persName>Moses Austin</persName>    [Rubric]</p>

<p>[Addressed:] <persName>Mr James. E B Austin</persName> <placeName>Nicholisville Kentucky</placeName></p>



        </div1>
